---
description: Python quality defaults for this repo.
alwaysApply: true
---
- Target Python 3.11+ and keep 3.13 compatibility.
- Prefer explicit Pydantic models and narrow modules.
- Default checks: `pytest -q`, `ruff check .`, `ruff format --check .`.
- If a command is not confirmed by repo evidence or a completed run, mark it `manual` instead of inventing a green check.
- Report pass, fail, or manual. Do not claim green when unverified.
- Follow the `AGENTS.md` output contract: summarize what changed; list files touched and commands run; state pass, fail, or manual verification; note assumptions and risks.
